ures\r\ncustomizability\r\nease of use\r\nsecurity\r\ntech (hardware) requirements\r\ncompatibility\r\ncompliance\r\nscalability\r\nperformance concerns\r\nlifecycle\r\nupgrades\r\n<p id=\"lVyfUvP\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-197 \" src=\"http://localhost/octomarketing.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/img_56e6249582543.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\nasdfasdf\r\n<h3>Step 2: Decide On Your Solution / Vendor List</h3>\r\nasdf\r\n<h3>Step 3:¬†Research, Demo, &amp;¬†Interview</h3>\r\nRFI (request for information)\r\nRFP/RFQ (request for quote)\r\n<p id=\"UYYIEiG\"><a href=\"/octomarketing.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/img_56e61c50cc0ae.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"wp-image-195 size-full aligncenter\" title=\"\" src=\"http://localhost/octomarketing.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/img_56e61c50cc0ae.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"829\" height=\"687\" /></a><img class=\"size-full wp-image-196 aligncenter\" href=\"/octomarketing.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/img_56e6236e9e96f.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Step 4: Evaluate Your Options</h3>\r\n<p id=\"ooPWMGQ\"><a href=\"http://localhost/octomarketing.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/img_56e615d5e82d8.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-193 size-full aligncenter\" href=\"/octomarketing.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/_d_improd_/img_56e615d5e82d8_f_improf_722x792.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"722\" height=\"792\" /></a></p>\r\nasdf\r\n<h3>Step 5: Seek Outside Opinions</h3>\r\nasdf\r\n<h3>Step 6:¬†Make Your Choice</h3>\r\nasdf\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"csColumnGap\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 3.12%;\"><img style=\"border: none;\" src=\"http://localhost/octomarketing.com/wp-content/plugins/advanced-wp-columns/assets/js/plugins/views/img/1x1-pixel.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"csColumn\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 31.3%;\" data-csstartpoint=\"15\" data-csendpoint=\"315\" data-cswidth=\"31.3%\" data-csid=\"46ed88e8-ab6c-1254-a760-36e1edf373d3\">\r\n<h2><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">WHAT?</span></h2>\r\nThis system will describe how to do a comprehensive review of a solution or vendor. Following this process will ensure that all due diligence is followed when choosing something that will be folded into the operational stack.\r\n<h2><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">WHY?</span></h2>\r\nObjectivism is about seeking the best possible option. One cannot be sure that the best possible option has been chosen unless all possible options are fairly reviewed.\r\n<h2><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">WHO?</span></h2>\r\nAt OctoMarketing the digital strategists and nodes of the strategic mind will conduct solution / vendor reviews.\r\n<h2><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">WHEN?</span></h2>\r\n<span class=\"transcript ga\" data-ga-action=\"click\" data-ga-label=\"toc-video-transcript\" data-duration=\"147.84\">This process should be used when making a solution / vendor decision that is going to have a significant impact</span><span class=\"transcript ga\" data-ga-action=\"click\" data-ga-label=\"toc-video-transcript\" data-duration=\"155.59\">. There are many instances when it would be more appropriate to make the decision without undergoing a formal review process. Depending on the scope and importance of the review the process can take an hour to weeks.¬†</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">HOW MUCH?</span></h2>\r\n<span class=\"transcript ga\" data-ga-action=\"click\" data-ga-label=\"toc-video-transcript\" data-duration=\"177.01\">Generally at least 5 alternatives and 5 criteria should be used, but the need is largely defined by the scope of the project.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">WITH WHAT?</span></h2>\r\n[button link=\"http://localhost/octomarketing.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Quantitative_Vendor_Comparison_Technique_for_RFP_or_RFI.pdf\" newwindow=\"yes\"]Download full vendor review PDF[/button]\r\n\r\nangieslist.com\r\ntop10r